  },
]

---

<LayoutPaginas title="Patagonia Courses | Ice Climbing Course" description="">
  <div class="container text-start px-3 px-lg-5">

    <Titulo title=' Patagonia Courses' />

    <div class="container text-center px-lg-5">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-auto col-lg-6 py-2 px-0">
          <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
            <ol class="breadcrumb my-2">
              <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a class="text-decoration-none text-body-secondary" href="/">Home</a></li>
              <li class="breadcrumb-item active"><a class="text-decoration-none text-body-secondary" href=/#courses>Courses</a></li>
              <li class="breadcrumb-item active"><a class="text-decoration-none text-body-secondary" href=/courses/ice-climbing-course>Ice Climbing</a></li>
            </ol>
          </nav>
          <h3 class="fs-3 fw-normal text-start text-body-secondary border-top pt-3">Ice Climbing and Glacier Travel Course</h3>
          <div class="texto fw-light ls-1 fs-5 text-start fst-italic text-body-secondary pe-0 pe-lg-4">
            <p>
              The objective of the course is to form and build a solid foundation in terms of technical and safety knowledge. The student will acquire the technical and individual skills required to travel in glacier areas. They will also obtain the technical skills to carry out a rescue and start in the world of ice climbing.</br>
              <b>Course duration:</b></br>
              - 5 full days in the field (morning and afternoon)</br>
              - 2 theoretical classes (within the first two days)
              </p>
              <a href="/itineraries/courses/IceClimbingCourse.pdf" target="_blank" class="fs-5 fw-normal link-secondary fst-normal text-body-secondary icon-link icon-link-hover link-offset-2-hover link-underline link-underline-opacity-0 link-underline-opacity-100-hover" role="button" aria-label="Download Itinerary">DOWNLOAD ITINERARY</a>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-file-arrow-down bi text-decoration-none ms-2"></i>
          </div>    
        </div>

        <Slider miArray={fotos} />

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</LayoutPaginas>

<style>
  .texto {
    font-family: "Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 1px; 
  }
</style>
